00:36:03.520 --> 00:36:07.380
But still, the point being
for both the historical time

00:36:07.380 --> 00:36:09.770
and the present time, yes, you
do get quite a lot of information

00:36:09.770 --> 00:36:12.330
from ships, but it's
very, very selective

00:36:12.330 --> 00:36:14.750
where you actually
have that information.

00:36:14.750 --> 00:36:19.190 position:56%
It's analogous really to the weather
