it's called, a reference level.

00:41:16.770 --> 00:41:20.050
And then by beaming a radar down,
it knows how much signal is sent.

00:41:20.050 --> 00:41:23.450
It times the time for it to come
back, the signal to come back.

00:41:23.450 --> 00:41:25.810
And then it can calculate the
path between the spacecraft

00:41:25.810 --> 00:41:27.110
