time, and then we might come

00:56:03.220 --> 00:56:05.850
up with slightly different
conclusions

00:56:05.850 --> 00:56:08.710
of how these things happen.

00:56:08.710 --> 00:56:11.510
You know, so I think those
are some of the things

00:56:11.510 --> 00:56:14.210
that I'm hoping we can use
NASA satellite observations

00:56:14.210 --> 00:56:15.510
to address in the future.

